by means of ...Bb7. Can White prevent Black from executing this idea?} 1. Na5
$1 {A very beautiful move which was discovered by Korchnoi in a blitz game
against Ulf Andersson. The critical line is:} Qxa5+ 2. Bd2 c3 3. bxc3 $1 Nd5 4.
c4 b4 5. cxd5 {White's advantage is obvious.} *

