act quickly.} 1. Ng5 $1 {White starts active operations anticipating the
thematic break ...c7-c5.} c5 2. Nc3 $1 {The knight emerges on the most natural
(although not so for this whole system) square, weakening Black's kingside
defence. White's idea can be seen in the following line:} h6 3. Nxd5 Bxd5 4.
Bxd5 exd5 5. e6 {With a simplification to an endgame which is favorable for
White.} *

